17:30.483 --> 17:32.450
Who is this doctor, dad?
I need to talk to him right now.

17:32.452 --> 17:33.818
I don't want to live here
anymore.

17:33.820 --> 17:35.186
Who is it?! Tell me!

17:35.188 --> 17:36.320
Katherine.

17:40.325 --> 17:42.293
I don't want to live anymore.

17:44.596 --> 17:46.831
I've made arrangements.

17:46.833 --> 17:49.333
It's my life.

17:49.335 --> 17:51.402
I just want to know
what my options are.

17:51.404 --> 17:53.171
I made an appointment
for Tuesday.

17:53.173 --> 17:54.739
I am going to Oregon.

17:54.741 --> 17:56.808
- You can't block this.
- Daddy?

17:56.810 --> 17:59.777
It's not your decision to make.

17:59.779 --> 18:01.379
Ray...

18:01.381 --> 18:05.850
Daddy, no, i...
I don't... I don't...

18:05.852 --> 18:08.252
Mom? Help me here...

18:08.254 --> 18:10.521
Sounds like he's got it
all worked out.

18:12.658 --> 18:16.127
He's not going to be eligible.
He's not dying.

18:16.129 --> 18:18.830
Maybe he just needs to know
what his options are,

18:18.832 --> 18:20.631
- once and for all.
- Okay, but, you know what?

18:20.633 --> 18:23.634
I'm not having some stranger
drive him, okay?

18:23.636 --> 18:27.205
Well, who else
do you have in mind?

18:27.207 --> 18:30.541
Don't even think about it.

18:41.787 --> 18:44.155
<i>Please just calm down.</i>

18:44.157 --> 18:46.724
<i>Stop telling me
to calm down, Brian, seriously.</i>

18:46.726 --> 18:48.893
Okay, could you explain to me
one more time

18:48.895 --> 18:50.561
why it has to be you
to drive him?

18:50.563 --> 18:52.530
I don't know, maybe if my mom
could stay sober

18:52.532 --> 18:54.599
for more than five fucking
minutes maybe she could do it.

18:54.601 --> 18:56.534
But she can't, so it's me.

18:56.536 --> 18:57.635
Maybe he doesn't
want to be saved.

18:57.637 --> 18:59.137
What are you talking about?

18:59.139 --> 19:00.471
I'm just trying
to get some perspective.

19:00.473 --> 19:02.807
Why would you say that?
Look, of course he does.

19:02.809 --> 19:05.643
Do you know how many people
his age who are dead or dying

19:05.645 --> 19:07.778
would give anything to spend
more time with their family?

19:07.780 --> 19:09.747
- Come on.

19:09.749 --> 19:11.415
What? What's so funny?

19:11.417 --> 19:15.419
I'm sorry, but that
doesn't sound like ray.

19:17.257 --> 19:20.358
Yes, hello?
Yeah, this is her mother.

19:22.928 --> 19:24.228
W-what?

19:28.201 --> 19:30.434
This is absolutely the last
thing I need right now!

19:30.436 --> 19:32.470
I'm never speaking to Colt
again, isn't that enough?

19:32.472 --> 19:34.205
Not. Even. Close.

19:34.207 --> 19:35.907
Do you understand
how serious this is?

19:35.909 --> 19:38.376
You sent those pictures!
You're underage!

19:38.378 --> 19:40.478
This could have been so much
worse than a suspension!

19:40.480 --> 19:41.779
They were private pictures!

19:41.781 --> 19:43.181
Jesus, nothing in
high school is private.

19:43.183 --> 19:45.249
- Give me your phone, by the way.
- No!

19:45.251 --> 19:47.218
- Get off!
- Stop, stop, stop, stop.

19:47.220 --> 19:48.786
You make me feel like
I'm such a freak!

19:48.788 --> 19:50.922
- Everyone does it!
- Everyone does not do it.

19:50.924 --> 19:53.257
And even if that was true,
it does not make it all right.

19:53.259 --> 19:55.393
They weren't even that bad!
You could hardly see anything!

19:55.395 --> 19:57.562
Do you care to weigh in
on this, please?

20:12.911 --> 20:14.845
- Hey.
- -Hey.

20:14.847 --> 20:16.681
What did you tell them?

20:16.683 --> 20:19.884
I told them that
you are not going anywhere.

20:19.886 --> 20:22.520
- Okay.
- That Annie needs you here.

20:22.522 --> 20:25.289
- Yeah, what about dad?
- Well, first I told him

20:25.291 --> 20:26.958
that he's not going to get
to Oregon by Tuesday.

20:26.960 --> 20:28.526
New York to Portland
in four days?

20:28.528 --> 20:29.627
Not gonna happen.

20:29.629 --> 20:32.530
