20:32.532 --> 20:34.365
when we don't have two children

20:34.367 --> 20:37.235
who are experimenting
in nude portraiture.

20:37.237 --> 20:39.003
- Oh, Jesus.
- Oh, baby.

20:39.005 --> 20:41.639
Why did this all
have to happen now?

20:41.641 --> 20:43.307
Why can't I just deal

20:43.309 --> 20:45.977
with one family catastrophe
at a time?

20:45.979 --> 20:48.479
Well, she's a teenager.

20:48.481 --> 20:51.249
Yeah, well,
what's his excuse, huh?

20:53.819 --> 20:57.321
I also called Danny,
and I left him a message.

20:57.323 --> 20:58.456
Why?

20:58.458 --> 20:59.924
Just...
I thought, you know,

20:59.926 --> 21:02.360
maybe he would be
the voice of reason.

21:02.362 --> 21:04.795
Why would you think that he...

21:04.797 --> 21:08.966
Danny can't take any more
of dad's shit, Brian!

21:08.968 --> 21:10.601
What are you doing?

21:10.603 --> 21:12.670
You can't just pawn
my father off on him.

21:12.672 --> 21:14.405
They don't even talk
to each other!

21:14.407 --> 21:15.773
