21:15.775 --> 21:17.408
He's my responsibility.

21:17.410 --> 21:18.643
I'm trying to find a solution!

21:18.645 --> 21:20.344
No! No, you're not!

21:20.346 --> 21:21.779
You're trying to get my parents
out of the house.

21:21.781 --> 21:23.447
That is exactly
what you're doing.

21:23.449 --> 21:25.283
Well, you know what,
it would be nice

21:25.285 --> 21:27.485
- to have the marriage back!
- This is our marriage, Brian!

21:27.487 --> 21:28.853
- This! All of this!
- No, no, no, no!

21:28.855 --> 21:31.555
This is not
what I signed up for!

21:31.557 --> 21:32.990
Oh, my fucking god.

21:36.662 --> 21:37.828
I'm sorry, I'm...

21:37.830 --> 21:40.731
Fuck, you're...
Oh, my god.

21:50.042 --> 21:52.343
Dad! Dad, please,
what are you doing?

21:52.345 --> 21:53.978
I don't have time to wait.

21:53.980 --> 21:56.414
I thought that you said
you cancelled the driver.

21:56.416 --> 21:59.016
I know what you're both doing.
It's not gonna work.

21:59.018 --> 22:01.385
- Brian?
- Hey, ray, ray, ray?

22:01.387 --> 22:02.887
I understand that you're upset,

22:02.889 --> 22:04.789
but you cannot do this
right now.

22:04.791 --> 22:07.925
